10
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:45,485
<font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>They will walk and not be faint.</i></font>

11
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:50,250
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Desmond, hang on!</font>

12
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:53,761
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hang on, Desmond!</font>

13
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:56,889
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We're going to get you out of here!</font>

14
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:14,722
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Desmond. Desmond!</font>

15
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,361
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What?</font>

16
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:19,444
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Wait up.
