238
00:22:33,600 --> 00:22:35,364
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Kiss me and find out.</font>

239
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:25,401
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What?</font>

240
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:28,609
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I have to enlist.</font>

241
00:23:29,800 --> 00:23:32,406
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I can't stay here while
