248
00:24:00,360 --> 00:24:02,200
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I don't know.
You still going to have me?</font>

249
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:05,403
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I wouldn't know,
you haven't asked.</font>

250
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:10,122
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I'm asking you,
