252
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:25,411
<font face="Comic Sans MS">When?</font>

253
00:24:25,480 --> 00:24:26,925
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Soon as you get your first leave.</font>

254
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:29,162
<font face="Comic Sans MS">But I still don't like you
