256
00:24:31,360 --> 00:24:33,806
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay. Well, I love you.</font>

257
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:36,008
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Shh!</font>

258
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:49,560
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Momma said come see you here.</font>

259
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:50,721
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah.</font>

260
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:57,087
<font face="Comic Sans MS">These 3 were my best friends.</font>

261
00:24:58,440 --> 00:25:00,920
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I grew up with 'em,</font>

262
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:03,000
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I got into trouble with 'em,
