263
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,240
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And I enlisted with 'em.</font>

264
00:25:07,760 --> 00:25:09,808
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Now my friends are there,</font>

265
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:14,563
