287
00:26:35,120 --> 00:26:36,400
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Ready?
- Ready.</font>

288
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:37,536
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Y'all need some air.</font>

289
00:26:37,560 --> 00:26:39,576
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on, fellas, shake a leg.
