290
00:26:39,600 --> 00:26:43,002
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Say goodbye to Momma. Come on.</font>

291
00:26:43,120 --> 00:26:45,487
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Ladies, please, step away from the bus.</font>

292
00:26:45,560 --> 00:26:48,370
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- I almost forgot. Here.
- Do I need a crowbar?</font>

293
00:26:49,080 --> 00:26:52,129
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I want you to have this.
It's mine.</font>

294
00:26:54,080 --> 00:26:57,562
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You keep it right here, where I'll be.</font>

295
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:04,008
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Bye.
- Bye.</font>

296
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:09,644
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I love you.</font>

297
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:49,128
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, don't say that about my girl.</font>

298
00:27:49,200 --> 00:27:50,770
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- What else...
