299
00:27:50,840 --> 00:27:53,161
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey. Sorry, pal.</font>

300
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:55,208
<font face="Comic Sans MS">...means you're the person.</font>

301
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:59,607
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- They got me a bum steer.
