303
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:05,371
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Gaze upon it in envy, my friend.</font>

304
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:11,568
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You okay there?
You look lost. Vacancy right here.</font>

305
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:15,087
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wise choice. It's got views of
