306
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,366
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Randall Fuller.</font>

307
00:28:17,680 --> 00:28:19,409
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Desmond Doss.</font>

308
00:28:19,480 --> 00:28:22,450
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Call him "Teach." No one
