00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:53,165
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, I didn't want to embarrass you.</font>

321
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:55,208
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wal Kirzinski, nice to meet you.</font>

322
00:28:55,280 --> 00:28:58,250
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, beanpole,
